GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_RhetoricalDevices> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_RhetoricalDevices> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#RhetoricalDevices> ;
    narr:childCount "18"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "516abc631ecd00f62ab1de218059ed731dc8819c" ;
    narr:narration """This hub catalogs rhetorical and stylistic devices observed across the corpus, spanning extended metaphor, aphoristic compression, anaphoric structure, antithesis, and recursive self-reference. The [optometrist as iterative review model](narr:StyleObs_OptometristMetaphor) anchors the product's explanatory logic — lenses, convergence rounds, \"better through A or B?\" — sustained across multiple sections. Alongside it, [arrows/archery as productivity argument](narr:Obs_FeatherArrowsClose) closes the flocking piece (Jul 2026), with a draft flag that the EV version should pivot toward the voices question rather than land on productivity. The [road/spatial and mathematical metaphors](narr:StyleObs_5) — asymptotic approach, escape valve, tools approaching a graph from opposite directions — frame epistemological and psychological concepts. Capitalized IS appears as a [spoken-word authority marker](narr:StyleObs_4) and as [aphoristic product principle](narr:StyleObs_CallIsMemory). Antithesis recurs as a core move — [\"not just\" inversions](narr:StyleObs_2), [\"running it, not evaluating it\"](narr:StyleObs_Antithesis), [\"It's not X, it's Y\" reframes](narr:StyleObs_VerbatimReframe). Anaphora structures both [identity claims](narr:StyleObs_Anaphora) and [imperative command sequences](narr:StyleObs_4). The [self-documenting release](narr:StyleObs_SelfDocumentingRelease) (Jul 5 2026) enacts a recursive rhetorical move — artifact describing itself as instrument. [Archetype testing](narr:StyleObs_ArchetypeTesting) (Apr 2026) and [methodology validation](narr:StyleObs_MethodologyValidation) (May 2026) mark earlier moments where principles were stress-tested against the full perspective. [Technical-register metaphors](narr:StyleObs_6) — \"bootload a new worldview,\" \"memories are like PRs\" — mark an idiolect layer distinct from the clinical optometry register.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_FeatherArrowsClose> ;
